'''Steam''' is een software-distributseplatförm die emaakt is deur [[Valve Corporation]] en is veural bedoeld veur [[Computerspöl|computerspöllen]]. Op [[12 september]] [[2003]] wier de eerste värsie uut ebracht met allenig as bedoeling um updates veur [[Counter-Strike]] makkelijker te mäken en te verspreiden.<ref>[https://store.steampowered.com/news/183/ Steam Client Released]. Valve Corporation (12 september 2003). </ref><ref>[https://www.valvesoftware.com/nl/ About Valve]. Valve Corporation.</ref> In [[2018]] had Steam al 90 miljoen maondelikse gebrukers die vaeke online waren. In 2019 waren dit er al 95 miljoen. In [[januari]] [[2019]] kwamp het 30.000 spöl op Steam.<ref>[https://steamcommunity.com/groups/steamworks/announcements/detail/1697194621363928453 Steam - 2018 Year in Review]. Steam (14 januari 2019).</ref><ref>[https://www.shacknews.com/article/109349/steam-now-has-30000-games-on-its-storefront Steam now has 30,000 games on its storefront]. Shacknews (14 januari 2019).</ref> 

Steam is de grootste platförm veur digitaole distribusie van computerspöllen met in [[2013]] een merktandiel van 75%.<ref>Edwards, Cliff (November 4, 2013). "[https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2013-11-04/valve-lines-up-console-partners-in-challenge-to-microsoft-sony Valve Lines Up Console Partners in Challenge to Microsoft, Sony]". ''[[:en:Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]]''. [https://web.archive.org/web/20141024081126/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-04/valve-lines-up-console-partners-in-challenge-to-microsoft-sony.html Archived] from the original on October 24, 2014. Retrieved November 5, 2013.</ref> In [[2017]] was 18% van de totaole wereldwiede computerspöllen via Steam ekocht: 4,3 miljärd [[Amerikaanse Dollar|dollar]].<ref>Bailey, Dustin (March 22, 2018). "[https://www.pcgamesn.com/steam-revenue-2017 With $4.3 billion in sales, 2017 was Steam's biggest year yet]". [[:en:PCGamesN|''PCGamesN''.]] Retrieved March 22, 2018.</ref>

De eerste värsie van Steam wier allenig uut ebracht veur [[Windows]].

